    <div class="apple-glass p-8 md:p-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white text-slate-900 mb-4">Try It Free</h2>
      <p class="dark:text-slate-400 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        SprintFlint includes 300 tickets free with no credit card required. Setup takes about 2 minutes. If you're running agile sprints and want clearer visibility into your team's velocity, give it a try.
      </p>
      <a href="https://sprintflint.com" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Get Started with SprintFlint
